nständige Positionen in diesen Kontexten darstellen. Mit Beiträgen von Jens Badura, Friedrich Balke, André Brodocz, Alex Demirovic, Alexander García Düttmann, Andreas Niederberger, Alice Pechriggl, Andreas Wagner und dem Frankfurter Arbeitskreis für politische Theorie & Philosophie.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAutonomie. 4aPolitik. 4aPolitikwissenschaft. 4aPolitikwissenschaften. 4aPolitische Philosophie. 4aPolitische Theorie. 4aPost-Marxismus. 4aPoststrukturalismus. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh  aPolitical Philosophy.  aPolitical Science.  aPolitical Theory.  aPolitics.  aPost-structuralism.1 aBadura, Jens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBalke, Friedrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrodocz, André, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDemirović, Alex, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDüttmann, Alexander García, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrankfurter Arbeitskreis für politische Theorie & Philosophie, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aNiederberger, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPechriggl, Alice, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWagner, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2000-2009z978311046334740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839402627zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839402627423Cover